  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah, welcome back! I imagine you’re wondering whether I was able to restore my map? Thanks to you I did, but... there's a bigger problem now."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "When I tried to follow the map back to my old home, the monsters became more savage as I went further. I had to retreat pretty quickly. Maybe it was too much for a small fairy like me from the start..."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Still, I don’t want to give up yet. If you could defeat the monsters west of the #m10006000# and thin their numbers, perhaps the path home would become safe enough. Could you help me once more?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you so much! The #r#o57#s#k and #r#o58#es#k west of #m10006000# seemed especially dangerous. If you can defeat them, I promise I will find a way to repay you."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "The #r#o57#s#k and #r#o58#es#k looked incredibly dangerous. I suppose even you might think it's too risky..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I was worried the whole time about whether you would return safely. But it seems you’ve managed to defeat them all."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I was right to trust you. I'm going to gather a few things and set out soon. I'm sure #p700# and #p702# will try to stop me, but if I leave quietly while they sleep, I should be able to go. Thank you, truly!"
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "sub"
        },
        "mob": {
          "_dirName": "mob",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "Please defeat the #r#o57#s#k and #r#o58#es#k west of the village to make the path to my old home safer. I’m counting on you."
          }
        }
      }
    }
